    "body": "Thanks for the PR, but actually you can use the [Menu.sendActionToFirstResponder](http://electron.atom.io/docs/v0.34.0/api/menu/#menu-sendactiontofirstresponder-action-os-x) method to achieve this:\n\n``` javascript\nMenu.sendActionToFirstResponder('hide:');\n```\n\nWe usually only add a new API with it is something that can not be done with existing tools, otherwise we would end up adding more than 30 new APIs for things under `NSApp`.\n"
